#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Distribution"
msgstr "Distribucija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the beginning of the game, countries are distributed to all the players. "
"Each country contains one army (represented by an infantryman) at the start. "
"Each player has some armies to distribute to his countries at their turn "
"(indicated by the presence of their name and their flag in the status bar). "
"Note that five armies are represented by a cavalryman and 10 by a cannon."
msgstr ""
"Na početku igre, zemlje se distribuiraju svim igračima. Svaka zemlja sadrži "
"jednu vojsku (koju zastupa pešadinac) na početku. Svaki igrač ima neke "
"vojske za distribuiranje njegovim zemalja na njegovom redu (ukazuje na "
"prisustvo njihovog imena i njihove zastave u status baru). Imajte na umu da "
"su pet vojski predstavljene sa konjanikom i 10 sa topovima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To put an army on one of your countries, click on it with the left mouse "
#| "button. To remove an army, click with the right button. Note, as a "
#| "general rule, that you will never be able to remove more armies than the "
#| "number you placed."
msgid ""
"To put an army on one of your countries, click on it with the &LMB;. To "
"remove an army, click with the &RMB;. Note, as a general rule, that you will "
"never be able to remove more armies than the number you placed."
msgstr ""
"Da bi postavili vojska na jednu od svojih zemalja, kliknite na nju s lijevu "
"tipkom miša. Da biste uklonili vojsku, kliknite na desnu tipku. Napomena, "
"kao opće pravilo, da nikada neće moći da uklonite više vojske od broja koji "
"ste smjestili."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Placing armies</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Postavljanje vojski</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Placing armies</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Postavljanje vojski</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a player has distributed all there armies, the next player is "
"automatically selected to do the same task. When all players have finished "
"to distributing their armies, there is two possibilities that can be "
"selected by two buttons showed in the right panel:"
msgstr ""
"Kada je igrač distribuirao sve svoje vojske, sljedeći igrač se automatski "
"bira da učini isti zadatak. Kada svi igrači završe distribucije svojij "
"vojski, postoje dvije mogućnosti koje se mogu odabrati na osnovu dvije tipke "
"prikazane u desnom panelu:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Redistribution"
msgstr "Redistribucija"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recycle"
msgstr "Recikliraj"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:255
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "One player wants to change some of his choices. The first player can then "
#| "remove an army he just put in a country with the right mouse button and "
#| "put it in another one with the left mouse button. When he finishes, he "
#| "gives control to next player with the <guibutton>Valid</guibutton> "
#| "button. When all players have finished their redistribution, the two "
#| "buttons are displayed again."
msgid ""
"One player wants to change some of his choices. The first player can then "
"remove an army he just put in a country with the &RMB; and put it in another "
"one with the &LMB;. When he finishes, he gives control to next player with "
"the <guibutton>Valid</guibutton> button. When all players have finished "
"their redistribution, the two buttons are displayed again."
msgstr ""
"Jedan igrač želi promijeniti neke od njegovih izbora. Prvi igrač tada može "
"ukloniti vojsku koju je on stavio na zemlji sa desnim klikom miša i staviti "
"još jednu sa lijevim klikom miša. Kada se završava, on daje kontrolu "
"sljedećem igraču sa <guibutton>Validan</guibutton>. Kada su svi igrači "
"završili svoje redistribucije, dva dugmeta se ponovo pojave."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "End of redistribution"
msgstr "Kraj redistibucije"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Done"
msgstr "Gotovo"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "The redistribution is finished and the game can continue."
